<h2>Who Should Use The Water Data Platform</h2>
<p>
The WEHUB is seeking members from all levels of government, industry, water-related researchers and non-government organizations, or those interested in innovation with water data, to help us create the largest source of water data on the Internet by uploading their water and environmental data. This focal point for water data will benefit government, industry, academia, and individuals seeking this information, as well as those looking to build customized applications on top of the web platform using our API.
</p>
